From: Jabbslad <jabbslad@gmail.com>
Subject: [PATCH] libipa: camera_sensor_helper: add SmartSens SC200PC

The SC200PC is a 2MP 1/3.06" Bayer sensor used by Samsung as
the ACPI SSLC2000 front camera on Panther Lake laptops
(e.g. Galaxy Book6 Pro NP940XJG-KGDUK). Without a helper entry,
the simple soft IPA logs:

    IPASoft: Failed to create camera sensor helper for sc200pc

and falls through to a code path that treats the raw V4L2 gain
code as a linear gain multiplier. For the SC200PC this leaves
AGC stuck near unity gain, producing severely underexposed
frames that AWB cannot converge on.

The SC200PC analogue gain register (0x3e09, exposed via
V4L2_CID_ANALOGUE_GAIN) is linear in 1/16 steps:

    code 0x10 -> 1.0x
    code 0x20 -> 2.0x
    code 0xff -> 15.9375x

giving the AnalogueGainLinear{ m0=1, c0=0, m1=0, c1=16 } model,
i.e. gain(code) = code / 16. Black level pedestal per the
SmartSens SC20x family is 64 at 10 bits, normalised to 4096 for
the 16-bit libipa scale (matches imx219 / imx214).

Also register static sensor properties so CameraSensorProperties
stops warning and the pipeline gets correct sensor delays and
unit cell size (1.75 um pixel pitch per SmartSens SC200 family
datasheet).

Signed-off-by: Jabbslad <jabbslad@gmail.com>
---
 src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp          | 12 ++++++++++++
 src/libcamera/sensor/camera_sensor_properties.cpp | 10 ++++++++++
 2 files changed, 22 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp b/src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp
index XXXXXXX..XXXXXXX 100644
--- a/src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp
+++ b/src/ipa/libipa/camera_sensor_helper.cpp
@@ -788,6 +788,18 @@ public:
 };
 REGISTER_CAMERA_SENSOR_HELPER("ov13858", CameraSensorHelperOv13858)

+class CameraSensorHelperSc200pc : public CameraSensorHelper
+{
+public:
+	CameraSensorHelperSc200pc()
+	{
+		/* From SmartSens SC20x datasheet: black level 64 at 10 bits. */
+		blackLevel_ = 4096;
+		gain_ = AnalogueGainLinear{ 1, 0, 0, 16 };
+	}
+};
+REGISTER_CAMERA_SENSOR_HELPER("sc200pc", CameraSensorHelperSc200pc)
+
 class CameraSensorHelperVd55g1 : public CameraSensorHelper
 {
 public:
diff --git a/src/libcamera/sensor/camera_sensor_properties.cpp b/src/libcamera/sensor/camera_sensor_properties.cpp
index XXXXXXX..XXXXXXX 100644
--- a/src/libcamera/sensor/camera_sensor_properties.cpp
+++ b/src/libcamera/sensor/camera_sensor_properties.cpp
@@ -493,6 +493,16 @@ const CameraSensorProperties *CameraSensorProperties::get(const std::string &sen
 			},
 			.sensorDelays = { },
 		} },
+		{ "sc200pc", {
+			.unitCellSize = { 1750, 1750 },
+			.testPatternModes = { },
+			.sensorDelays = {
+				.exposureDelay = 2,
+				.gainDelay = 2,
+				.vblankDelay = 2,
+				.hblankDelay = 2
+			},
+		} },
 		{ "vd55g1", {
 			.unitCellSize = { 2160, 2160 },
 			.testPatternModes = {
